title: Lauzon Leads 'Hounds to Twin Ports Win
text:
Lauzon Leads 'Hounds to Twin Ports Win 
By Zach Schneider October 6, 2015 Updated Oct 6, 2015 at 11:07 PM CDT 
Duluth, MN (NNCNOW.com) --- Alyssa Lauzon finished with a match-high 15 kills on Tuesday night as the Duluth East volleyball team earned a 3-0 sweep over Twin Ports rival Superior. 
Daisy Hoops added eight kills in the winning effort, while Alayna Baker finished with 34 set assists and Maya Callaway had 25 digs.
